I think transformers couldnt back in Generation 1, but after the great war 
they borrowed some things from the humans, including size, age, and 
reproduction.  I think it does have to do with the spark.  I think the female 
gets a binary spark, with hers and the childs, and they program a body.  This 
seems to be the most logical explanation.
